name: Khan-Ur's Flame
description: <c=@flavor>"I always had trouble jumping from the tree to the ruins. Then my daughter found another path on the southern shore."</c>

name: Stone Summit Shoulder Box
description: Open to choose a set of Stone Summit shoulder armor.

name: Perspective of the Ascalonian Wall
description: <c=@flavor>"Separatists on one side, ghosts on the other. Too many dead charr."</c>

name: Gift of the World
description: In the Mystic Forge, combine a Gift of the World with a Mist Band, a Mystic Tribute, and a Gift of Conquering to create Conflux.

name: Prototype Harmonizing Mist Loom

name: Steel Warband Banner Skin

name: Confrontation

name: Faint Echo of Whispers

name: Preparation

name: Dark Wing Axe Skin

name: Red Prophet Crystal
description:
Crystalline formations of dragon magic, veined with red.
Emissaries in the Eye of the North have interest in these.
Obtained from Priority Strikes or by combining shards.

name: Stone Summit Glove Box

name: Faint Echo of Forging Steel

name: Record

name: Broken Rod
